{
  "info": {
    "name": "RentNest API",
    "description": "Complete API documentation for RentNest - Rental Property Marketplace\n\nBase URL: {{base_url}}/api\n\n## Authentication\n- Register/Login to get a JWT token\n- Token is auto-set to `token` variable\n- Protected routes require `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}` header\n\n## Variables\n- `base_url`: API base URL (default: https://rentnest-api.vercel.app)\n- `token`: JWT token (auto-set after login/register)\n- `propertyId`: Store after creating/looking up a property\n- `rentalRequestId`: Store after creating a rental request\n- `paymentId`: Store after creating payment intent\n- `transactionId`: Store after creating payment intent\n- `reviewId`: Store after creating a review\n- `categoryId`: Store after creating/looking up a category\n- `userId`: Store for admin operations",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "rentnest"
  },
